
PICsim - PIC Simulator

This is the lcsim directory tree:

examples         - Examples
gui		 - Graphic User Interface using wxwidgets
lab              - Picsimlab


Requirements:

wxwidget 	- For graphic suport		   http://www.wxwidgets.org
wxdevcpp	 -For compile picsim in windows    http://wxdsgn.sourceforge.net 

Pic16fxx supported hardware:
	Interrupts
	WTD
	TMR0
	TMR1
	TMR2
	USART
	CCP1 ->PWM (8bits)
	CCP2 ->PWM (8bits)
	EEPROM
	IO PORTS


Utils:

com0com		- For serial emulation in windows  http://com0com.sourceforge.net/ 
ttypatch	- For serial emulation in linux    http://ttypatch.sourceforge.net/
gputils		- For assemble examples            http://gputils.sourceforge.net/
sdcc		- For compile examples             http://sdcc.sourceforge.net/
piklab		- IDE for edit examples            http://piklab.sourceforge.net/






